column2: Have you experienced tinnitus lasting more than 2-3 minutes?
Have you experienced tinnitus for at least 6 months?
In a quiet room, can you hear tinnitus?
When you heard tinnitus this past year, was it caused by a recent event? (Examples: loud concert, head cold, allergies, some medications)
Does your tinnitus seem to "come and go" on its own, in addition to being caused by a recent event(s)?
How frequently do you experience tinnitus?
